Root Layout:(in simple agr aap chahte ho ki aapki app k andr hr page pr ek layout show ho then use this )
Global elements jaise header, footer, aur common styling ke liye use karo jo har page pe dikhna chahiye.


Multiple Layouts: (agr aap chahte hr ek leaf segment ki alg layout ho then use this)
Different sections jaise dashboard, profile, ya login ke liye alag layouts banane ke liye use karo, jahan har section ki apni specific design aur elements hote hain.
In short, root layout har page pe same elements rakhta hai, aur multiple layouts alag-alag sections ke liye different designs handle karte hain.

